---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { href } from "@/utils/paths";
---

<BaseLayout title="404 · 페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다" description="페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다" noIndex>
  <section class="flex min-h-[60vh] flex-col items-center justify-center text-center" aria-labelledby="error-heading">
    <span class="ghost-404 heading-page text-8xl sm:text-9xl" aria-hidden="true">404</span>
    <h1 id="error-heading" class="heading-page mt-4 text-2xl sm:text-3xl">페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다</h1>
    <p class="secondary-copy mt-3 text-base">
      찾으시는 페이지가 존재하지 않거나 이동되었습니다.
    </p>
    <p class="muted-copy mt-2 text-sm">아래 경로로 돌아가 보세요.</p>
    <nav class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3" aria-label="복구 링크">
      <a href={href("/")} class="btn-accent">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
        </svg>
        홈
      </a>
      <a href={href("/start-here/")} class="btn-ghost">읽기 경로</a>
      <a href={href("/posts/")} class="btn-ghost">전체 글</a>
      <a href={href("/tags/")} class="btn-ghost">태그</a>
    </nav>
    <p class="search-hint mt-6 text-sm">
      특정 글을 찾고 계셨다면 상단의 검색 버튼이나 <kbd>⌘K</kbd> / <kbd>Ctrl K</kbd>로 검색해 보세요.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .ghost-404 {
    color: var(--border);
  }
  .secondary-copy {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  .muted-copy {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .btn-ghost {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.1rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .search-hint {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .search-hint kbd {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
  }
</style>
